      <title>KKR 利润因资产销售改善而飙升，超出预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/kkr-profit-soars-49-on-improving-asset-sales-beating-estimates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[KKR &amp; Co. 公布第二季度利润超过华尔街预期，因为该收购公司通过出售资产获得的收入超出预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/kkr-profit-soars-49-on-improving-asset-sales-beating-estimates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 10:56:50 GMT</pubDate>
