      <title>印度最大汽车制造商盈利超预期 计划每年推出一款电动汽车</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/maruti-suzuki-beats-profit-forecast-driven-by-surge-in-suv-sales</link>
      <description><![CDATA[玛鲁蒂铃木有限公司公布季度利润好于预期，得益于其运动型多用途车销量增长，该公司计划每年推出一款电动汽车。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/maruti-suzuki-beats-profit-forecast-driven-by-surge-in-suv-sales</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 10:01:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
